title: JUI-F leader calls on PM Shehbaz Sharif
content:
ISLAMABAD, Jul 9 (APP): Leader of Jamiat Ulema-e-Islam Fazl (JUI-F) and former federal minister Maulana Asad Mehmood Wednesday called on Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif and discussed matters of mutual interests.
During the meeting they discussed the overall political situation of the country.
Maulana Asad Mehmood also paid tribute to the prime minister for achieving economic stability in the country.
